My obsession with @valentino.beauty is REAL💖
.
Valentino Beauty Puffer gloss: new lip gloss that gives you extra plump, extra shine & extra care. 
- Hyaluronic Acid: Helps retain moisture for visibly plump, hydrated lips.
- Vitamin E and Ceramide: Soften skin for lips that feel nourished.
.
Valentino Donna Born In Roma Perfume Intense: 
 a magnetic floral ambery, pushing vanilla and jasmine into a captivating embrace to glorify magnificent personalities. I like this one better than the original, as the scent is more intense and long lasting. 
.
Valentino Born In Roma Uomo Extradose: 
fougère woody ambery men’s fragrance, an extradose of vetiver, amplified by intensely spicy notes and lavandin for an extra-seduction. Perfect gift for the special guy in your life. 🖤
.
.
